{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1716760/extras/Combo_600x240_Framed_Optimized.gif?t=1727837127\" /><br><br><strong>Trinity Archetype</strong> is a roguelite, turn-based RPG where you fight deadly enemies trying to take over your broken world.<br><br>Customize and create unique party builds, analyze upcoming actions to plan your own, and use the unique Skill Boost and Party Inspire mechanics to get the upper hand in battle. Every run is different!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1716760/extras/Header_Inspire.png?t=1727837127\" /><br>Once per turn, a party member can inspire their allies in order to activate new interesting effects. Inspiring at the right moment can turn the battle around in your favor!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1716760/extras/Inspire_600x240_Framed_Optimized.gif?t=1727837127\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1716760/extras/Header_Boost.png?t=1727837127\" /><br>Power-up your skills during battle by spending Boost Points! Each skill has extra effects depending on your boost level.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1716760/extras/Boost_600x420_Framed_Optimized.gif?t=1727837127\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1716760/extras/Header_Customization.png?t=1727837127\" /><br>Level up your characters and unlock new skills after each battle then further enhance them by equipping Runes and unleash their full potential! There are millions of possibilities to try!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1716760/extras/Rune_Customization_600x240.gif?t=1727837127\" /><br